                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.14278/2605.14278v1/x3.png",
                "caption": "Figure 2:Overview of theKVPOtraining pipeline.Starting from a shared initial noise, the model first performs causal-semantic exploration via stochastic KV routing within a perturbed window to produce diverse candidate branches (a). These branches are then replayed under the unperturbed deployment-time context, where the Trajectory Velocity Energy of each branch is computed and converted into Gibbs-form surrogate branch probabilities to measure their generation likelihood under the current policy (b). Finally, the branches are scored by the reward model, and PPO updates the AR generator toward higher-reward behaviors via a contrastive flow-matching objective (c)",
                "position": 417
            },
